    public class NumberFieldExpression<T extends java.lang.Number,X extends DataObject>
extends FieldExpression<T,X>
    A FieldExpression for Number values. This supports Integer, Long, , Float and values.

    Duration objects are stored at millisecond resolution so as to properly implement SQLExpression to store values at a different resolution use a DurationFieldValue.
